text: Arizona Bushwhackers is a 1968 American western movie directed by Lesley Selander and starring Howard Keel, Yvonne De Carlo, John Ireland, Scott Brady, Marilyn Maxwell, Montie Montana. It was distributed by Paramount Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1968 movies Category:1960s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Lesley Selander Category:Paramount Pictures movies
